{
  "texts": [
    "These results underscore the effectiveness of RL in enhancing the reasoning capabilities of LLMs.",
    "As well as the progressive enhancement of reasoning capabilities during training, DeepSeek-R1-Zero also demonstrates self-evolutionary behaviour with RL training.",
    "As shown in Fig. 1b, DeepSeek-R1-Zero exhibits a steady increase in thinking time throughout training, driven only by intrinsic adaptation rather than external modifications.",
    "Making use of long CoT, the model progressively refines its reasoning, generating hundreds to thousands of tokens to explore and improve its problem-solving strategies.",
    "The increase in thinking time helps with the autonomous development of sophisticated behaviours."
  ]
}